title: The Friday Morning Conversation With Tim McGraw + Producer Eddie Attempts To Figure Out Who Bobby's Dating
itunes:title: The Friday Morning Conversation With Tim McGraw + Producer Eddie Attempts To Figure Out Who Bobby's Dating
description:
Tim McGraw stopped by to talk about his new music for the Friday Morning Conversation. Eddie tries to get Lunchbox to tell him who Bobby's been dating. Also, Bobby shares the next song he'll be dancing to on Dancing With The Stars.
